archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.name: CMS Site Core Third Party To Be

children.content: Cloud Information Security Strategy is under development 2016
Caution: Gartner have warned that Sitecore's cloud offeing is currently 'minimal'

Search -there may be a need for a new enterprise wide search if the standard search from SharePoint and/or the new CMS is not good enough.
Depending on where search needs to act it could be cloud-based.

KEY ASSUMPTIONS:
- intranet replaced by CMS
- international websites replaced by CMS
- links from CMS enable students and staff to access key systems e.g. SITS, Blackboard, Career Hub, this with personalisation means CMS can replace myUWE portal
- data from CRM, Alumni, SITS systems used to drive personalisation,
Data warehouse is enhanced to include website data and enable additional analyses.
